{"id": 2857, "genre": 1001, "title": "出现啥状况，就意味着“这家店的寿命，对我来说已经终结了”？", "description": "“再也不来了”的一百个理由。", "record_count": 4477, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190321131403cvpfiJU5RC9n6MLO.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-03-22T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 335104, "content": "店员竟然给我推荐过期产品？就因为我当时只有8岁？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1575834}, {"id": 335105, "content": "菜单刚拿到，还没翻完呢，点菜员说，您先看，点好了再叫我。\n生意太好了吗？下次不来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616411}, {"id": 335106, "content": "本地商业广场陆续关了八家饭店  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 321342}, {"id": 339970, "content": "牛展", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1640574}, {"id": 335107, "content": "饭店-难吃、衣服-不适合自己、酒店-脏、其他的就是贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1590940}, {"id": 335876, "content": "分量越来越少", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1620535}, {"id": 335110, "content": "贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1270483}, {"id": 335113, "content": "店员态度恶劣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379220}, {"id": 335114, "content": "我们在一起吧", "image": "img/option/option/20190323093859CbRMAhErOiSytILv", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616491}, {"id": 335115, "content": "我的天啊撸啊撸", "image": "img/option/option/20190323093915wYN8fPMljdOWzoAV", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616491}, {"id": 335886, "content": "难吃价格还贵店员还一脸娇气意思\"买不起吧穷鬼\"搞得自己很高端一样，封杀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603624}, {"id": 335119, "content": "口气极差，爱答不理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616415}, {"id": 335631, "content": "产品质量差，服务态度恶劣，环境脏乱差", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619106}, {"id": 335120, "content": "口气极差，爱答不理", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616415}, {"id": 335888, "content": "鸡肉饭里有鸡骨头", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1603980}, {"id": 335121, "content": "我对你纯纯的爱恋，你都不让我打包。哼，拜拜了您咧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616506}, {"id": 335122, "content": "卫生问题", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139320}, {"id": 335634, "content": "难吃还贵 新店就环境差 服务也不到位 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1619204}, {"id": 335123, "content": "排队等半天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1139320}, {"id": 335124, "content": "贵", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1136760}, {"id": 335125, "content": "卫生", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1592407}, {"id": 335129, "content": "老板在打麻将 东西让我自己拿", "image": "img/option/option/201903231109157qFmwxieP3JdYkA8.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1310565}, {"id": 335131, "content": "当我觉得这次消费明显不值得的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335747}, {"id": 336156, "content": "店员的态度不好", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1621848}, {"id": 335134, "content": "服务态度差，难吃。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616609}, {"id": 335136, "content": "态度冷淡，食物不新鲜，环境差，桌子擦不干净", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1470841}, {"id": 335139, "content": "妈耶……看了你们的评论 店员真难干……随便站在那干什么都会灭了一家店……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1201350}, {"id": 336677, "content": "服务态度差，即便好吃也不来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1623513}, {"id": 335398, "content": "纸巾质量特别差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1600473}, {"id": 335143, "content": "看什么东西店员就盯着你\n你动一动就翻白眼", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616680}, {"id": 335144, "content": "“淡淡的”不好吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1438159}, {"id": 335145, "content": "遇到一个你很喜欢的人，你要怎么办？", "image": "img/option/option/2019032314353648tcG5DNFl9HqAEd.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1605497}, {"id": 335146, "content": "服务态度恶劣", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054974}, {"id": 335147, "content": "进店没人招待客人", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615971}, {"id": 335148, "content": "有人抽烟，而服务员在场却不作为！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1571144}, {"id": 335151, "content": "去到一个会员店里，用会员号付的钱，但是他没有帮我充会员的积分😡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616753}, {"id": 335152, "content": "难吃", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616755}, {"id": 335154, "content": "“妹妹，好久没看到你了”", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616780}, {"id": 335155, "content": "服务态度差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1423008}, {"id": 335156, "content": "卫生差   口味差  环境差", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616796}, {"id": 335158, "content": "比预期的结果要差很多，产生失望的感觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616793}, {"id": 335161, "content": "在基本同时进店的情况下，因为你是高中生而对你的服务态度变得很随意，甚至抛之于脑后，根本没把你当回事。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616849}, {"id": 335162, "content": "半天叫不到服务员的店", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1443830}, {"id": 335163, "content": "爱答不理，口气狂妄\n其他都可以忍受", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1614643}, {"id": 335164, "content": "有一次我和我朋友穿着校服去吃饭，服务人员对我们视而不见 听而不闻，有种被歧视了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615434}, {"id": 335165, "content": "当小料理店换了师傅后，我就不会再去了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1616866}, {"id": 335168, "content": "不能选 不辣 或者 微辣 或者 微辣也很辣 的餐馆", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399413}, {"id": 335170, "content": "找钱的时候特别慢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1153779}, {"id": 335172, "content": "服务不礼貌 味道不合口", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1615113}, {"id": 336453, "content": "对我来说，只有腻了，或者涨价了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1622744}]}